---
title: Pozole-Inspired Veggie Stew with Plant-Based Protein and Toasted Pepitas
description: Pozole is a Mexican stew, traditionally made with pork and hominy corn. For our veggie twist, we replaced them with plant-based patties, sweet corn kernels and tortilla chips!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/ragout-de-legumes-facon-pozole-09160e70.jpg
